{"tid":1202370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"群龍無首的解決方法","createTime":"2019-06-11T08:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T11:06:25.000Z","uid":135770,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a9931cd1d95cf4e80708345980706e54371d36","tid":1202370,"uid":135770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:58:28.000Z","msg":"要解決群龍無首嘅問題<br />\n就係group 埋幾個leader 一齊傾共識（當然和理非就收收皮先）<br />\n所以而家連登統戰部正式想搵外交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n負責contact 其他組織 同一啲相應ig or fb page<br />\n建立訊息網 作統戰之用 為求盡快號召同散播信息<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NUxMSBTF8-cq2lseswnGgw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNUxMSBTF8-cq2lseswnGgw&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=9ef1ef54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NUxMSBTF8-cq2lseswnGgw</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣人士要有以下要求：<br />\n1. 正常  非民陣式和理非<br />\n2.識人 eg(眾志等組織成員 contact)<br />\n3.具影響力 eg 人脈廣 or 自己搞緊page"},{"pid":"befb11fb0a31d918fcc14f409793add47bde68a5","tid":1202370,"uid":135770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:10:50.000Z","msg":"認真組織化🙏 推"},{"pid":"0cd9ca91de6393e6c6b7ed660de9692de89e57dd","tid":1202370,"uid":15395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36fcdff167fe92b8c0d416cc3e7a26cd8b2b5707","tid":1202370,"uid":216380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:01:50.000Z","msg":"到時真係要好好保護領軍人 <br />\n唔可以有機會比到警方係對抗結束前拉林低 <br />\n同埋各地都分應該多啲真係了解今次我地決心同做法既人 去解釋比和理非聽 始終和理非佔極大多數<br />\n<br />\n最好一條街距離最少一個可以知道流程 目的既人帶個 喇叭去講下 咁樣最有效"},{"pid":"427f0b34a307e89d469c59d239def341e9550bf3","tid":1202370,"uid":216380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36fcdff167fe92b8c0d416cc3e7a26cd8b2b5707","tid":1202370,"uid":216380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:01:50.000Z","msg":"到時真係要好好保護領軍人 <br />\n唔可以有機會比到警方係對抗結